{"tid":1647541,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"【極緊急】跪求十八區各自最大籃球街場名單！！","createTime":"2019-10-11T19:44:01.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-12T17:22:32.000Z","uid":53610,"like":31,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":40,"replies":[{"pid":"3c384e94985fe2425074fecaf61827899141e255","tid":1647541,"uid":53610,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T19:44:01.000Z","msg":"NBA風波對香港極具意義，我哋絕對應該好好把握依個機會嚟connect美國人，搞個聲援NBA活動，具體理由喺依個post有講<br />\n<br />\n【和理手足入】NBA事件好好運用至少贏到一個月國際輿論<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1639013\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1639013</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n我知道有巴打已經搞緊全港籃球賽，但係就要多一排先安排到，然而我想講件事已經冇得再拖，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">兵貴神速，時不我予</span></span><br />\n<br />\n再拖多排我驚個國際焦點會愈來愈遠，所以我決定緊急倡議今個星期日先舉行個<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">全港籃球迷大和解集會</span></span><br />\n<br />\n地點唔需要喺啲要預約的場，用返街場就得，所以我想先問下各位巴絲打，關於十八區各自最大/最適合搞大和解的街場大家有冇咩建議？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n決定好場地之後我會即刻開post正式宣傳依個活動同討論個詳情，希望喺聽晚前趕得切搞文宣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1e63bb91cbcd54a052457d059bedbd638e0a66f1","tid":1647541,"uid":304512,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T19:47:10.000Z","msg":"上水紅場"},{"pid":"e75246e692ef6916707c5f6108675ff62de0ee2d","tid":1647541,"uid":53610,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T19:48:29.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"30f6de8fb4214d3052bd300dd82bba3520817de9","tid":1647541,"uid":269515,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T19:54:18.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">全球「和尼畫」<br />\n#XinniethePooh Challenge</span></span></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1640322/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1640322/page/1</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/search?q=%23XinniethePooh&amp;src=typeahead_click\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fsearch%3Fq%3D%2523XinniethePooh%26src%3Dtypeahead_click&d=bDN9RnBWsu2ZFehd%2BUm4uMemYpZY8oJkMX6FO%2BQoeBQ%3D&h=d122f3e2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/search?q=%23XinniethePooh&amp;src=typeahead_click</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/t0UOaVn.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ft0UOaVn.png&h=c7fd48b9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1yAhQxD.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1yAhQxD.png&h=d230a326&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n「和尼畫」挑戰<br />\n1.畫出你心中所想的維尼圖<br />\n2.留下你想對習維尼講嘅說話<br />\n3.放上ig、fb、twitter，tag #XinniethePooh<br />\n4.tag 1-3個你想佢一齊畫維尼嘅朋友<br />\n5.被tag嘅朋友一齊畫維尼，讓愛與維尼佔領地球，推到畀習維尼本人見到<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n&quot;Xinnie the Pooh&quot; Challenge<br />\n1. Draw your own &quot;Xinnie the Pooh&quot;<br />\n2. Write down what do you want to tell Chairman Xi<br />\n3. Post your work on ig, fb and twitter with tag #Xinniethepooh <br />\n4. Tag up to 3 more friends to draw together!"},{"pid":"892d03e3a269a9db3cc939cfd68e409ddbd57af4","tid":1647541,"uid":53610,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T19:55:46.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"7ceca723b7c5a3663a83f997302a558cac8ced12","tid":1647541,"uid":269515,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T19:55:51.000Z","msg":"諗法幾好<br />\n但純和理非活動其實閒日夜晚做就得？<br />\n同埋而家吹星期日雞比較難<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/think.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"088f06fef2038821a7f7417366208979b8649bfc","tid":1647541,"uid":53610,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7ceca723b7c5a3663a83f997302a558cac8ced12","tid":1647541,"uid":269515,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score"